You've Been Invited!
==================

Hi <%= @invitee_name %>,

<%= @inviter_name %> has invited you to join <%= @account_name %> on <%= app_name %>.

Accept your invitation by visiting:
<%= @invitation_url %>

Invitation Details:
-------------------
Account: <%= @account_name %>
Role(s): <%= @role_names %>
Invited by: <%= @inviter_name %>
Expires: <%= Time.parse(@expires_at.to_s).strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") rescue @expires_at %>

What Happens Next:
------------------
1. Click the invitation link above
2. Complete your account registration
3. Set your password
4. Start collaborating with your team!

Note: This invitation will expire on <%= Time.parse(@expires_at.to_s).strftime("%B %d, %Y") rescue @expires_at %>. Please accept it before then.

If you believe you received this email in error, you can safely ignore it.

Best regards,
The <%= app_name %> Team
